Citation.sAbstract: Volumetric and viscometric properties of the binary mixture of hexan-1-ol with m-xylene at T = (303.15, 313.15, and 323.15) K have been investigated. The excess volumes and viscosity deviations from the mole fraction average were calculated and correlated by a Redlich-Kister type equation.
Citation.sTitle: Thermodynamic Properties of the Binary Mixture of Hexan-1-ol with m-Xylene at T = (303.15, 313.15, and 323.15) K
